need: claim any amount instead of all at once. will require more talk between app and contract
can proxy this contract for future improvements too
instead of PUT requests from chainlink to update app, could use API that reads contract events such as https://bitquery.io/blog/ethereum-events-api

How often do tax rates need to be updates, and by what source, i.e. should chainlink handle the rate modifications too every so often? another potential keeper application in addition to the claim receipt

Additions needed to proxy this contract, too...

